dollar, is now redeemable for about $0.74 worth of USDC and about $0.00 wor=
th of TITAN, which does not add up to a dollar.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">Of course it adds up to $0.74, which is something. In a purely algorit=
hmic stablecoin, the stablecoin=E2=80=99s peg to the dollar is maintained b=
y issuing and redeeming some other coin =E2=80=94=C2=A0called the =E2=80=9C=
share token=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94=C2=A0that fluctuates in value; the idea is t=
