<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">require(_share_price &gt; 0, =E2=80=9CInvalid =
share price=E2=80=9D);</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">_share_price here re=
fers to the price of TITAN, as provided by an oracle, which is correctly re=
porting it as=E2=80=A6 <strong>0</strong> (somewhere in the distance, you c=
