<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">TITAN dropped from 65$ to 30$ in 2 hours, whic=
h later recovered in 1 hour to 52$ and IRON fully recovered its peg. =E2=80=
=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Later, at around 3pm UTC, a few big hol=
