2><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Sure, why not:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"ma=
rgin: 16px 0;">Using lottery jackpot winnings within neighborhoods as exoge=
nous shocks, we examine whether feeling lucky affects retail stock purchase=
